high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the wall, then turn left and walk up to the shower, turn left again to face the toilet.
Pick up the closest black spray bottle off of the toilet tank.
Turn left and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the sink.
Put the black spray bottle on the counter to the right of the sink.
Walk back over to the toilet.
Pick up the black spray bottle off of the toilet tank.
Walk back over to the sink counter.
Put the black spray bottle on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move two spray bottles to the counter.

high_descs: Go to the toilet
Pick up the spray bottle from the toilet
Go to the sink
Place the spray bottle down to the right of the sink
Go to the toilet
Pick up a second spray bottle from the top of the toilet
Go to the sink
Place the spray bottle down to the left of the sink
anns.task_desc: Move two spray bottles from a toilet to a sink

high_descs: Move in front of the toilet to your right.
Pick up the bottle of cleaner on the far right.
Move to the bathroom vanity on your left.
Put the bottle of cleaner on the counter to the right of the sink.
Move back to the toilet on your right.
Pick up the bottle of cleaner on the far right.
Move back to the bathroom vanity on your left.
Put the bottle of cleaner on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move two bottles of cleaner to the bathroom vanity.
